thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Diane A Rosner

author: Diane A Rosner
title: Diane A Rosner
text: Having spoken with Jennifer, issues are being resolved. She was extremely pleasant and helpful. This is not my first order from Frames Direct and, now, I am sure that I will be just as happy with my second pair. I do recommend their outstanding service and personal relationship with their customers.
